            <run fontalignment='1'>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontalignment='1' fontcolor='#a36599' fontname='Helvetica' fontsize='20'>Workers&apos; Welfare and Burnout</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </title>
      </layout-options>
      <style />
      <size sizing-mode='automatic' />
      <zones>
        <zone h='100000' id='4' type-v2='layout-basic' w='100000' x='0' y='0'>
          <zone h='55310' id='35' is-fixed='true' type-v2='layout-basic' w='55342' x='615' y='933'>
            <zone h='55310' id='14' param='horz' type-v2='layout-flow' w='39997' x='615' y='933'>
              <zone h='55310' id='10' param='vert' type-v2='layout-flow' w='39997' x='615' y='933'>
                <zone fixed-size='68' h='8868' id='11' is-fixed='true' type-v2='title' w='39997' x='615' y='933'>
                  <zone-style>
                    <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
                    <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
                    <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
                    <_.fcp.DashboardRoundedCorners.true...format attr='corner-radius' value='5' />
                    <format attr='margin' value='4' />
                    <format attr='background-color' value='#f7f1f6' />
                  </zone-style>
                </zone>
                <zone h='46442' id='12' name='Burnout Score vs. Hours Worked/wk' w='39997' x='615' y='9801'>
                  <layout-cache minheight='215' minwidth='159' type-h='scalable' type-w='scalable' />
                  <zone-style>
                    <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
                    <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
                    <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
                    <_.fcp.DashboardRoundedCorners.true...format attr='corner-radius' value='10' />
                    <format attr='margin' value='4' />
                    <format attr='background-color' value='#f3ebf3' />
                  </zone-style>
                </zone>
              </zone>
            </zone>
            <zone h='55310' id='36' param='horz' type-v2='layout-flow' w='15345' x='40612' y='933'>
              <zone fixed-size='212' h='55310' id='13' is-fixed='true' param='vert' type-v2='layout-flow' w='15345' x='40612' y='933'>
                <zone fixed-size='83' h='10618' id='15' is-fixed='true' name='Burnout Score vs. Hours Worked/wk' pane-specification-id='4' param='[federated.14fqtqb0t0xbcc14yfkgo0z6qybt].[none:Work_Mode:nk]' type-v2='color' w='15345' x='40612' y='933'>
                  <zone-style>
                    <format attr='border-color' value='#d4a6c8' />
                    <format attr='border-style' value='solid' />
                    <format attr='border-width' value='3' />
                    <_.fcp.DashboardRoundedCorners.true...format attr='corner-radius' value='5' />
                    <format attr='margin' value='4' />
                    <format attr='background-color' value='#fbf7fb' />
                  </zone-style>
                </zone>
                <zone fixed-size='60' h='7934' id='16' is-fixed='true' name='Burnout Score vs. Hours Worked/wk' param='[federated.14fqtqb0t0xbcc14yfkgo0z6qybt].[none:Work_Mode:nk]' type-v2='highlighter' w='15345' x='40612' y='11551'>
                  <zone-style>
                    <format attr='border-color' value='#d4a6c8' />
                    <format attr='border-style' value='solid' />
                    <format attr='border-width' value='3' />
                    <_.fcp.DashboardRoundedCorners.true...format attr='corner-radius' value='5' />
                    <format attr='margin' value='4' />
                    <format attr='background-color' value='#f3ebf3' />
                  </zone-style>
                </zone>
                <zone fixed-size='221' forceUpdate='true' h='26721' id='19' is-fixed='true' type-v2='text' w='15345' x='40612' y='19485'>
                  <formatted-text>
                    <run fontcolor='#b07aa1'>Based off of the trend lines, it can be seen that </run>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#b07aa1'>remote workers are less likely to burn out over longer working hours</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#b07aa1'>. The opposite effect is seen for Onsite Workers.</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#b07aa1'>However, </run>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#b07aa1'>hybrid workers tend to have a lower average burnout score</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#b07aa1'> past a normal number (40) of hours worked.</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;&#10;&#10;</run>
                  </formatted-text>
                  <zone-style>
                    <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
                    <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
                    <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
                    <format attr='margin' value='4' />
                  </zone-style>
                </zone>
              </zone>
            </zone>
          </zone>
          <zone h='42824' id='25' is-fixed='true' type-v2='layout-basic' w='55342' x='615' y='56243'>
            <zone h='42824' id='20' param='horz' type-v2='layout-flow' w='40037' x='615' y='56243'>
              <zone h='42824' id='22' name='Regions &amp; Work Life Balance' w='40037' x='615' y='56243'>
                <layout-cache cell-count-w='7' minheight='152' non-cell-size-w='52' type-h='scalable' type-w='cell' />
                <zone-style>
                  <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
                  <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
                  <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
                  <_.fcp.DashboardRoundedCorners.true...format attr='corner-radius' value='10' />
                  <format attr='margin' value='4' />
                  <format attr='background-color' value='#f3ebf3' />
                </zone-style>
              </zone>
            </zone>
            <zone h='42824' id='26' param='vert' type-v2='layout-flow' w='15305' x='40652' y='56243'>
              <zone h='13418' id='24' name='Regions &amp; Work Life Balance' synchronized='1' type-v2='currpage' w='15305' x='40652' y='56243'>
                <zone-style>
                  <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
                  <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
                  <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
                  <format attr='margin' value='4' />
                </zone-style>
              </zone>
              <zone forceUpdate='true' h='24737' id='27' type-v2='text' w='15305' x='40652' y='69661'>
                <formatted-text>
                  <run bold='true' fontcolor='#b07aa1'>Use the toggles above to toggle the work setup type (i.e. Remote, Hybrid, Onsite). </run>
                  <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                  <run fontcolor='#b07aa1'>Remote has the highest average work life balance rating out of all the setups (indiscriminate of the region), with a significant difference, demonstrating that </run>
                  <run bold='true' fontcolor='#b07aa1'>remote work arrangements provide better work life balance opportunities for employees.</run>
                  <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                </formatted-text>
                <zone-style>
                  <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
                  <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
                  <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
                  <format attr='margin' value='4' />
                </zone-style>
              </zone>
            </zone>
          </zone>
          <zone h='98134' id='21' param='vert' type-v2='layout-flow' w='43428' x='55957' y='933'>
            <zone fixed-size='181' h='21120' id='33' is-fixed='true' param='vert' type-v2='layout-flow' w='43428' x='55957' y='933'>
              <zone fixed-size='141' forceUpdate='true' h='17386' id='34' is-fixed='true' type-v2='text' w='43428' x='55957' y='933'>
                <formatted-text>
                  <run fontcolor='#b07aa1'>After putting the data through a machine learning model (Random Forest Classifier), the model concludes that the </run>
                  <run bold='true' fontcolor='#b07aa1'>factors that contribute most to worker burnout are the hours worked per week, and the remote setup satisfaction. </run>
                  <run fontcolor='#b07aa1'>The classifier also notes that work mode is the least significant factor for worker burnout.</run>
                </formatted-text>
                <zone-style>
                  <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
                  <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
                  <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
                  <format attr='margin' value='4' />
                </zone-style>
              </zone>
            </zone>
            <zone h='77014' id='32' name='Feature Importances for Burnout ' w='43428' x='55957' y='22053'>
              <layout-cache cell-count-w='5' minheight='296' non-cell-size-w='63' type-h='scalable' type-w='cell' />
              <zone-style>
                <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
                <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
                <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
                <_.fcp.DashboardRoundedCorners.true...format attr='corner-radius' value='10' />
                <format attr='margin' value='4' />
                <format attr='background-color' value='#fbf7fb' />
              </zone-style>
            </zone>
          </zone>
          <zone-style>
            <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
            <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
            <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
            <format attr='margin' value='8' />
          </zone-style>
        </zone>
